description: Gentle tea rose, lilac, Calla Lily, and Somalian Rose layered over golden Peruvian amber, Spanish moss, red sandalwood, rosewood, and myrrh, with the lightest touch of Mandarin.

name: Violets and Creme
description: Simple, beautiful, elegant and oh so delicious; candied violets and rich mounds of homemade marshmallow fluff and fresh sweet cream.

name: Viridis Arcanum
description: A dark green mystery of Turkish galbanum incense resin, Russian leather, and the fresh tips of coniferous Siberian forest greens.

name: Vitality
description: Bright mandarin, Italian lemon, bergamot, may chang flower, golden sandalwood, ginger co2.

name: Vixen
description: Oleander, Jasmine, Rose petals, Cashmere, Coconut milk, Tonka Bean, Cypress, Texas Cedar, Sandalwood, Bourbon Vanilla, Oakmoss

name: Vixen
description: Lascivious, flirtatious, and vampy as hell. A true heartbreaker's perfume. The innocence of orange blossom tainted by the beguiling scents of ginger and patchouli.

name: Voila!
description: cream soda and bourbon, simple enough and one of my favorite high balls to watch my fav retro uhhh, films, too…

name: Volcano
description: A beautiful marriage of light clean florals and citrus notes. If you have ever been in Anthropologie you have smelled this delicious scent. They burn the candle called Volcano as their signature brand scent all the time. Now you can wear it.

name: Voodoo
description: A midnight scent, evoking images of flickering golden firelight reflecting off the sheen of glistening skin and the jerking shadows of bodies suffused with spiritual ecstasy. A deep, powerful, resonant blend of myrrh, patchouli, vetiver, lime, vanilla, pine, almond and clove.

name: Voodoo Queen
description: Black cardamom, saffron, sage, rose, jasmine, palo santo, cedar.

name: Voyance
description: A wreath of meadowsweet, elderflower, cornflower, verbena, waterlily and other summer solstice flowers gently floating on ethereal waves of clean water musk.

name: Vulpecula
description: Pools of rainwater, soaked pebbles, tomato leaf, decaying tree bark, wild brambles, dusty fur

name: Waffle Cone
description: Sweet toasted sugery goodness.

name: Wally Wallaby
description: Elderflower Blossom, Australian Lily, Strawberry, Musk, White Raspberry, Bastet's Amber infused Pear skin

name: Water of Notre Dame
description: Brings peace to the spirit, a sense of calm and fulfillment, and attracts the aid of beneficial spirits.

name: We Are Stars
description: An explosion of bright fruit notes of fresh orange, ripe mango, and southern peaches, All pulled back together again by the delicate sweetness of white gardenia, muguet, night blooming jasmine, blonde sandalwood, and sweet vanilla musk.

name: West Indian Vanilla
description: Rich aspects of Vanilla Ice Cream essence, an ethereal French Vanilla Fleck, Vanilla Buttercream, beautiful on its own or layered with Crystalline, a touch of Kobalt, a little French Vanilla...there can never be too many Vanilla perfumes.

name: Wetlands
description: A scent for reminiscing about visiting the wetlands. Brackish water and vegetation with honeysuckle, water lily, Spanish moss, aloe vera, and a touch of sassafras

name: Wheatstacks, Snow Effect, Morning
description: Hay, white peach, opalescent musk, orris root, pink carnation, osmanthus, and rooibos.

name: Wheel of Fortune
description: Cotton Candy, Candied Apple, Buttered Popcorn, Sticky Caramel, Wood Smoke, Vanilla

name: When the Shadows Burn Brighter than Embers
description: Dusty desert sand under an aging afternoon sun, lavender and sweet grass wafting in the air surrounding the Smokey remnants of a recently deceased fire. Smoke and ash surround the perfumed woman, who smells of slight spice and Black musk

name: When Tigers Smoked Pipes
description: Warm fur, pipe smoke, temple incense, roasted barley tea

name: Whinnies: Twenty-Three
description: Marshmallow with neroli, blackberry, and vanilla.

name: Whinnies: Two
description: Marshmallow with peony, yellow mandarin, and sandalwood.

name: White Cake
description: Vanilla-infused white cake with a fine, delicate crumb. This is equally sweet but less rich and dense than Arcana's Yellow Cake.

name: White Musk
description: clean, slightly soapy skin, powdery white florals, light vanilla.

name: White Pear Crystalline
description: Egyptian White Pear Accord, African Mandarin Essence, a quiet drop of Vanilla of Crystalline and Vanilla of Moonstone

name: White Tea
description: An elegant, crisp almost linen like fragrance.

name: Who Needs Love
description: A mahogany box filled with chocolaty orbs, coated in crystallized coffee, filled with a pomegranate and raspberry filling

name: Wig Reveal Wig Spray
description: A panoply of layered hues: champagne with a twist of white ginger, peach, raspberry pulp, and orange flower absolute.

name: Wiggly Worm Dance Party on Funky Fresh Cake
description: Fluffy yellow chiffon cake with marshmallow cream icing, topped with candied mints and sprigs of fresh lavender. They are having a funky fresh time.

name: Wild Strawberry Rosewater
description: A burst of sweet, fresh wild strawberries overlaid with the delicate fragrances of fresh distilled rosewater, dewy miniature rose petals, and spring rain kissed leaves. Wild Strawberry Rosewater is a simple, happy fragrance made with a blending of natural aroma accords.

name: Willowbrook
description: The Willowbrook is no more, but you can recapture some of the magic when you wear this complex and celebratory scent, laced with notes of blackberry, talc, midnight rain and Egyptian sandalwood.

name: Windsong
description: Vanilla Sugar, Pink Musk, Cotton Candy, Strawberry Lollipops

name: Wings of an Angel
description: Hawthorn, white musk, a touch of ethereal mintiness, gorgeous regal vanilla Bourbon.

name: Winter Warlock
description: Astro red poinsettia, whispering wind, twisted candy cane and melting vanilla ice cream

name: Witch Glow
description: Black iced tea accord, blackest blackened berries, black summer plums, mandarin petit grain, cardamom, magnolia, and witch's glow accord.

name: Witch Please
description: Whatever that witch is brewing up in her cauldron, it's definitely not for the faint of heart! Boozy bourbon barrel-aged Cabernet and vanilla cream ale.

name: Witch's Cottage
description: Warm Baked Goods, Dried Herbs, Sweet Annie, Soft Woods, Fragrant Hearth Smoke.

name: Witches Brew
description: As a witches brew should be ... the notes of this scent are mysterious! Cinnamon bark blended with warm, spooky spices and a splash of citrus.

name: Witches Fly Through The Forest with Sasquatch
description: The scent of a forested joyride on besoms. A knapsack stuffed with graham crackers, gooey marshmallows, and dark chocolate for making s'mores over the fire. Tree tops, black pinewood, delicate juniper branches, black spruce, Atlas cedarwood. A sliver of orange peel and a bit of fur.

name: Witchiepoo
description: Clove, aged vanilla, green greasepaint, pumpkin, sugar cubes, hint of scorched sugar.

name: Wobanakik V2
description: No notes. See my "Reviews" tab for description.

name: Wolf Spirit
description: Desert Sage, Pinyon Pine & Resin, Conifers, Cedar, Vetiver, Palo Santo, Soft Incense, Frankincense, Fur & Juniper

name: Wolf's Heart
description: Grants courage under extreme conditions, helps overcome fear of death, and strengthens the fortitude of artists and businessmen, enabling them to further their goals.

name: Wonderful Christmastime
description: Crème de menthe, crushed candy canes, and spearmint create the coolest, crisp mint accord. Vanilla cream and marshmallow fluff make it extra delicious.

name: Wood and Cotton
description: Great big tufts of clean cotton and a base of beautiful, dark wood.

name: Wood Carver
description: Cedar and oud wood spiked with clove, peppercorn, and smoked vetiver with a finish of amber resin, aged bourbon and vanilla and a touch of sweet wood smoke.

name: Wuthering Heights
description: lavender, vanilla, spectral musks, vetiver, tonka, jasmine, tea leaves, oakmoss.

name: Xavier
description: Amber accord, Balsam of Peru, Vanilla extract, Myrrh, Cedarwood, Sandalwood, White Musk, Red Pine, Elemi, Lotus blossom and French Vanilla

name: Xiuhtecuhtli
description: Copal, plumeria and sweet orange and the smoke of South American incense and crushed jungle blooms.

name: Ydalir
description: Mysterious, smoky, and primal. A 100% natural scent of Megalithic ancestral memory - 35 million year old fossilized amber resin, oakmoss absolute, Siberian Black Pine, smoked Juniper tar, and balsam pine needles preserved in a base of pure, cold pressed Meadowfoam seed oil.

name: Year Without Summer
description: the narcotic sweetness of opium blended with the blackest amber, spilled coffee, a hint of bitter green cannabis

name: Yellow Bunny
description: Japanese White Lily, Cassis essence, Musk, Bastet Amber, Peach essence and Bastet Musk

name: Yesterday Haze
description: Fig, Iris, Cream, Tonka, Tree Bark, Walnut Bitters, Orchard Dust

name: Ygritte
description: A thick cloud of Egyptian musk drifting from the stall of an outdoor market on an overcast afternoon. Coconut milk bought from a vendor hung with pikake flowers, as you rest in a field of sunflowers against an oak tree gazing at the bodies of your enemies.

name: YKW? IDEK
description: Sparkling aldehydes, raspberry essence, apricot, pink peppercorn, meadow grass, papaya, vanilla, spun sugar.

name: You Tempt Me
description: Vanilla custard, marzipan, sweet cherries, a hint of pastry crust, ambery notes

name: Youthful
description: Is a blend of cream soda and skin milk it's has the essence of a soda cream musk! Not overly sweet and very layer worthy to add a soft non-aldehydic creamy sparkle to scents. I feel as a preteen I always wore some vanilla bullshit and I am still quite the vanilla bullshit fan!

name: Yuletide Blessings 2019
description: An incantation of offerings to welcome the return of the sun and bring blessings for 2020 - boozy fruitcake studded with glace cherries, candied pineapple, citron, candied ginger, dates, and brown sugar; gilded citrus peel for luck; balsam pine for health and protection; cinnamon and clove for friendship; bayberry for wealth; tonka for love; golden amber and Omani frankincense to welcome the new year.

name: Zarita, the Doll Girl
description: Soft, yet sociopathic: white carnation, iris, orange blossom, poisonous pale white berries, and sugared cream.

name: Zazz
description: When something feels a bit lackluster, dull and boring, it obviously is lacking zazz. To fix this we recommend something definitely zazzy and not overly complicated: Tart cranberry, pink grapefruit, sparkling champagne all shook up with crushed ginger root.

name: Zephyr
description: A gentle white scent, breezes laced with the scent of springtime blooms and citrus. Lemon, lemon verbena, neroli, white musk, white florals, white sandalwood, China musk, bergamot and a drop of vanilla.

name: Zodiac: Scorpio
description: Zodiac: Scorpio ~ Vanilla Cream, Bastet's Zamsara Incense, Kobalt (Vanilla Orchid of Cairo), Egyptian Blue Sugar, Deep Red Musk, N3 (an Egyptian Musk) and aged Black Amber.

name: Zoe and the Goat
description: Caramelized patchouli, cream, and thick golden honey.

name: Zorya Polunochnaya
description: Pale amber and ambergris, gossamer vanilla, moonflower, and white tobacco petals.

name: Zozimus
description: Fresh floofy marshmallow fluff.

name: Zozismus
description: fresh floofy marshmallow fluff
